        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-3",
        "text": "It is also known as a celebration of America and a loose list of poems representing his philosophy on life.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 26
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 28.393
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-4",
        "text": "He cheered people up during the Civil War and wrote many other inspiring poems like “O Captain! My Captain!” about Abraham Lincoln.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 20
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 2.699,
          "y_px": 39.187
        },
